Text: Hyah!
Hmph...!
Stay back...
Hah...!
Stay...further back.

...That's right. Throwing swords blindly isn't how
it's done. If you want to defeat an opponent, one
precise strike should be enough.

I use multiple swords to ensure that one critical
hit lands...!
If you can't hit me, it's meaningless!

But it creates a distance between us... This
distance is better for me...

(Lady Eta...is closely observing Lady Alpha's
movements.)

(She grasps that Lady Alpha is overwhelmingly
superior in overall strength, so she's attempting
to fight under conditions more favorable to her.)

Once Lady Alpha gets within your range, she'll
skillfully control and maintain the distance between
you and her...!

I heard she hit you with a powerful headbutt.
Is that true?
...Yes.
How did it feel?

That one hit was enough to kill Lady Karen. In other
words, it hurt like hell.
Pfft...!

...Lady Alpha is ruthless towards her opponents.
So are Lady Delta and Lady Eta, but she's in a class
of her own.

Aside from Master Shadow, she really is in
a different class.

...By the way, how long do you plan to cling onto
this scale?

Until the fight is over...I guess? Even Lambda is
just quietly observing.
Seriously, Omega—

At this point, there's pretty much no way for anyone
to interfere in the duel between Lady Alpha and Lady
Eta, is there?
...Same goes for that battle over there.
Nooooo!!! I can't stop "swish, swish, swish"-ing!

Whoa... Gamma, your hits are landing a lot more
than usual!

You've gotten stronger...but I'm much, much
stronger!!!
S-Someone stop meeeeeee!!!
True...you might be right, but...

You always take things too seriously. Learn to slack
off a bit.

...You may sound convincing, but you just want to
laze around, don't you?
Yup, pretty much. So what?

H-How can you be so brazen...?! I won't accept that
side of you—
Shh! Things are taking a turn!
...Hah!

(Nicely done! Lady Alpha used the slime sword Lady
Eta threw as a foothold to close the distance...and
get behind her!)
...Out of my way!

If you're just going to throw them at random,
I might as well use them like this to get behind you.
You're moving just like Olivier...!

Pulling off spur-of-the-moment moves like that
defies all logic...!

It's not spur-of-the-moment. It's the result of
daily diligence.
Come on, time to give up, Eta!
I will secure the budget and personnel...!

(...The next clash will likely determine the outcome
of this battle.)
(But...there's no time left!)
